_sText:
After few months of improving beta version of this map I can proudly release another map inspired by real location 

Features: 

  • HDR 
  • 3D skybox
  • soundscapes (office, assault)
  • Easter HE eggs on office floor :D
  • randomly spawned hostages
  • broken walls and barriers in halls
  • allowed access to exterior
  • few obstacles in exterior
  • custom models of Skoda cars
  • few custom textures
  • fixed navigation map by Will2k

Thank you all bananas.

If you like this one, check all of my maps here
This map or its parts is also used in my singleplayer mod

Have a fun
Dinus Saurus
